## Exercise: Explore, Clean, and Wrangle Data

load packages
```{r}
library(readr)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(tidyr)
```

read in the data
```{r}
lobster_traps <- read_csv("../data/Lobster_Trap_Counts_All_Years_20210519.csv")

```
exploration
```{r}
colnames(lobster_traps)
head(lobster_traps)
unique(lobster_traps$OBSERVER)
unique(lobster_traps$FISHING_SEASON)

```
